@startuml
title Weather Station State Transition Diagram

state "Shutdown" as Shutdown
state "Running" as Running
state "Configuration Mode" as ConfigurationMode
state "Controlled Mode" as ControlledMode

Shutdown --> Running : Power-up

Running --> ConfigurationMode : Changes required
Running --> ControlledMode : Remote control
Running --> Shutdown : Shutdown command
Running --> Running : Data collection (triggered by clock)
Running --> Running : Summary request
Running --> Running : Status request

ConfigurationMode --> Running : Configuration completed

ControlledMode --> Running : ?

Shutdown --> [*] : Shutdown

[*] --> Shutdown : Power failure

@enduml
